#. Tag: para
#: security_ad_support.xml:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "However, Unix attributes can still be managed manually when <guimenu>Advanced Options</guimenu> are enabled in the <emphasis>Active Directory Users and Computers</emphasis> MMC snap-in. For more information, see <link xlink:href=\"https://blogs.technet.microsoft.com/activedirectoryua/2016/02/09/identity-management-for-unix-idmu-is-deprecated-in-windows-server/\"/> ."
