#. Tag: para
#: security_ad_support.xml:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "Alternatively, use the method described in <xref linkend=\"pro-security-ad-join-sssd\"/> to complete attributes on the client side (in particular, see <xref linkend=\"st-security-sssd-home-dir\"/> )."
